hadiths[39]{hadithnumber,text}:
4240,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein (khutba deney ke liye) khadey huey. aapney apney is maqam par qiyamat tak jo honey wala tha sab bayan kiya aur us mein se kuchh na chhoda. yaad rakhney waley ne usey yaad rakha aur bhoolne waley ne usey bhoola diya. yaqinan merey un sathiyon (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba) ko wo yaad hoga aur jab un waqiyat mein se koi pesh aata hai to mujhey wo sab yaad aa jata hai jaisey kisi ko kisi ke chaley janey ke baad uska chehra yaad rehta hai phir muddat baad jab usey dekhta hai to usey pehchan leta hai.
4241,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is ummat mein chaar fitney hongey aur unke baad duniya fana ho jaeygi.''"
4242,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they. aapney fitnon aur aazma-ishon ka zikr farmaya aur bahut tafsil se bayan kiya yahan tak ke aapney ihlaas ke fitney ka bhi zikr kiya. to kehney waley ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ihlaas ka fitna kya hai? aapney farmaya : ''bhaagam bhag aur gharat giri ! phir wusat aur faraakhi (maal aur zar) ka fitna aaeyga jis ka zuhoor merey ehale-bait ke eik fard ke paon taley se hoga. uska da'wa hoga ke wo mujh se hai halanke wo mujh se nahin hoga. bila-shuba merey wali aur dost sirf muttaqi log hain. phir log eik aadmi par suleh kar lengey jaisey ke peeth ho pasli par ! (yani naa-ma'qool aur naa-ahal hoga jis tarah ke peeth eik paslii par nahin tik sakti.) phir eik fitna uthey ga ghata-top andhera, is ummat mein se koi nahin bachey ga magar usey uska tamaancha pad kar rahega. isliye jab samjha jaeyga ke ye fitna khatam ho gaya wo aur badh jaeyga. aadmi subah kerega to momin hoga aur shaam hogi to kafir ho jaeyga yahan tak ke log do khemon (fariqon) mein taqseem ho jaeyngey. eik khema emaan ka . . . jis mein koi nifaq nahin hoga. . . aur doosra nifaq ka jis mein koi emaan na hoga. . . aur jab ye ahwaal (haalaat) hon to dajjaal ka intizar karna. aaj aaya ki kal.''"
4243,"Saiyedna Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya Allah ki qasam ! main nahin janta ke merey sathi haqeeqatan bhool gaey hain ya bholey baney huey hain. Allah ki qasam ! duniya khatam honey tak aaney waley fitnon ke qaaidain jinkey sath teen-sau ya us se ziyada log hongey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi ko nahin chhoda hai. aapney unke naam , unke baapon ke naam aur unke qabeelon tak ke naam bata diye hain."
4244,"Sabee'a bin Khalid ne bayan kiya ke jis zamaney mein (khoozistaan mein) tustar ka ilaaqa Fateh hua main koofa aaya. main yahan se khachchar hasil karna chahta tha. main masjid mein chala gaya to maine wahan chand aadmi dekhay jin ki qaamat aur jasaamat mutwassit (beech ki) qism ki thi , aur (sath hi) eik aur aadmi bhi baitha hua tha, jisey dekh kar aap keh saktey they ke ye hijaazi aadmi hai. maine puchha ke ye kon hai? to logon ne naa-pasandeedgi ke se andaz se dekha aur kaha : kya tum unhen nahin jantey ho? ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi Huzefa bin Yamaan hain.  (Raziallahu anhu)  . . phir Huzefa ne bayan kiya ke deegar Sahaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se khair ke mutalliq puchha kartey they aur main aap se shar ke mutalliq sawal kiya karta tha (ke kahin us mein mulawwis na ho jaun) to un logon ne unko ghaur se dekha. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main khoob samajhta hun jo tumhen bura lagta hai. maine arz kiya tha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye khair jo Allah ne hamen inayat farmaee hai kya uskey baad shar hoga jaisey ke is se pehley tha? aapney farmaya : ''haan.'' maine arz kiya : to us se bachao kya hai? aapney farmaya : ''talwaar.'' Quteba ne apni riwayat mein kaha : main (Huzaifa) ne arz kiya : kya talwaar se koi faeyda hoga? farmaya : ''haan.'' maine arz kiya ke kya? farmaya : ''suleh hogi jis mein (بباطن) khayanat hogi dhoka hoga.'' maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! iskey baad kya hoga? aapney farmaya : ''agar zameen mein Allah ka koi khalifa ho aur wo tumhari kamar par maarey aur tumhara maal chheen ley tab bhi uski itaat karna. warna us haal mein mar jana ke tum (jangal mein) kisi darkht ki jad chabaa kar guzaara kerney waley hon.'' maine arz kiya : phir kya hoga? aapney farmaya : ''dajjaal aaeyga, uskey paas nehar hogi aur aag. jo uski aag mein pada uska ajr Sabit hua aur uskey gunah khatam huey aur jo uski nehar mein pada uskey gunah Sabit huey aur ajr zaya ho gaey.'' maine arz kiya : phir kya hoga? aapney farmaya : ''phir qiyamat aa jaeygi.''"
4245,"Khalid bin Khalid Yashkari ne ye hadees riwayat ki, is mein hai ke Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke . . . talwaar ke baad (kya hoga?) aapney farmaya : ''kuchh log baqi bachen gey jinkey dilon mein fasad hoga. b-zahir suleh karengey magar baatin mein dhoka hoga. . . ''phir hadees bayan ki. kaha ke Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) is hadees ko Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ke ehade-khilaafat mein pesh aaney waley fitne irtidad (islam se fir jane) par mahmool (khayal) kiya kartey they. (اقذاء ‏ , قذى) ki jama hai. us tinkey ko kehtey hain jo aankh mein pad jata hai. (هدنة) ka maani suleh . . . aur (دخن) ka maani hai seeney ka bughz jalan aur kudhan."
4246,"Nasar bin Aasim Laisi ne bayan kiya ke ham bano Lais ke chand log Khalid bin Khalid Yashkari ke yahan gaey. unhoney puchha aap kon log hain? ham ne bataya ke bano Lais se hain. ham aap ki khidmat mein Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees maloom kerney ke liye hazir huey hain. to unhoney wo hadees bayan ki, kaha ke ham (banu Leis ke log) Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath wapis lautey. jabkey koofa mein janwar (khachchar waghaira) mehnge they. to main aur merey sathi ne Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se ijazat chahi to unhoney hamein ijazat dey di. to maine apney sathi (Nasar bin Aasim) se kaha ke main masjid jata hun aur jab mandi shuru hogi, main tumharey paas aa jaunga. kehtey hain ke main masjid mein dakhil hua to dekha ke wahan eik halqa laga hua hai, goya unke sar katey huey (pure dhiyan se) , eik aadmi ki baat badey ghor se sun rahey hain. main bhi un mein ja khada hua to eik aadmi merey pehlu mein aa khada hua . maine puchha , ye kon hai? usney kaha : kya tum Basra ke ho? maine kaha, haan . usney kaha : main jaan gaya hun, agar tum koofa ke hotey to is shakhs ke baarey mein na poochhtey. chunanche main us guftgu kerney waley ke qarib ho gaya (aur wo Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) they) to maine Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, bayan kar rahey they ke log to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se khair ke baarey mein poochhtey they aur main shar ke baarey mein sawal karta tha. aur mujhey yaqeen tha ke main khair se mehroom nahin rahun ga. maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya is khair ke baad shar hai? aapney farmaya : ''aey Huzefa ! Allah ki kitab seekh (aur padha kar) aur jo us mein hai uski perwi kar.'' aapney ye teen baar farmaya. kehtey hain ke maine phir daryaft kiya, aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya is khair ke baad shar hai? aapney farmaya : ''aey Huzefa ! Allah ki kitab seekh (aur padha kar) aur jo us mein hai uski ittiba kar.'' aur hadees bayan ki . . . is mein hai. . Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya is khair ke baad shar hoga? aapney farmaya : ''fitna hoga aur fasad hoga.'' kehtey hain : maine puchha aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya us shar ke baad khair hogi ? aapney farmaya : ''aey Huzefa ! Allah ki kitab seekho aur jo us mein hai uski ittiba kartey raho.'' teen baar farmaya. kehtey hain : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya us shar ke baad khair hogi? farmaya : ''suleh hogi khayanat wali. ittifaq aur ijtima hoga magar kadoorat wala'' . . . maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! (الهدنة على الدخن) se kya murad hai? aapney farmaya : ''logon ke dil pehley ki si keyfiyat par wapis nahin aaeyngey.'' kehtey hain, maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya us khair ke baad shar hoga? farmaya : ''fitna hoga andha aur behra. aur iskey quaid dozakh ke darwazon ki taraf dawat deney waley hongey . . . to aey Huzefa ! agar tum is haal mein mar jao ke tum kisi darkht ki jad ko chabaaney waley ho to ye kaifiyat tumharey liye us se behtar hogi ke un mein se kisi ki ittiba karo.''"
4247,"Sabee'a bin Khalid ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum un dinon mein koi khalifa na pao to bhag jana yahan tak ke mar jao. aur agar tumhari maut us haal mein aaye ke tum kisi darkht ki jad chabaaney waley huey (to ye behtar hoga).'' kehtey hain, maine arz kiya : uskey baad kya hoga? aapney farmaya : ''agar kisi ne chaha ke uski ghodi bachcha janey , to wo bachcha nahin jann paey gi ke qiyamat aa jaeygi .'' (yani bahut jald aisa hoga.)"
4248,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi Imam ki baiat ki ho aur apney haath ka maal aur dil ka phal (apna qol aur qarar) usko dey diya ho to phir himmat bhar uski itaat karey. agar koi doosra (ameer bin kar) aaye aur us se jhagda karey to us doosrey ki gardan maar do.'' (Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain) maine Abdullah bin Amr se puchha : kya bhala ye hadees aapney khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hai? farmaya (kyon nahin) isey merey kanon ne suna aur dil ne yaad rakha hai. maine kaha : ye aap ka chacha zaad Muawiya hamein hukm deta hai ke yun keren aur yun keren? kaha : Allah ki itaat mein uski itaat karo aur Allah ki gunah mein uski nafarmani karo.
4249,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''halakat hai arbon ke liye, us shar se jo qarib aaya chahta hai, kamiyab hai wo jisney apna haath rokey rakha.''"
4250,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' an-qareeb musalmanon ko Madina mein mahsoor kar (gher) liya jaeyga aur unki amal-daari ziyada se ziyada (khaibar ke qarib) maqame salaah tak hogi.''"
4251,Zohri ne bayan kiya ke ''salaah'' khaibar ke qarib eik maqam ka naam hai.
4252,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beshak Allah taala ne merey liye zameen ko lapetaa aur maine iski mashriqon aur maghribon ko dekha aur bila-shuba meri ummat ki amal-daari wahan tak pahunchey gi jahan tak usey merey liye lapetaa gaya hai, aur mujhey surkh aur safed (sona chaandi) do khazaney diye gaey hain. aur maine apney Rab taala se sawal kiya hai ke meri ummat ko aam qehat se halak na farmaai aur in par inke apney andar ke alawa bahir se koi dushman musallat na ho jo inhen halak karkey rakh dey. to merey Rab ne mujhey farmaya : ''aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! main jab koi faisla karta hun to usey radd nahin kiya jata. main (teri ummat ke) in logon ko aam qehat se halak nahin karunga aur inke apney andar ke alawa bahir se koi dushman musallat nahin karunga jo inhen halak karkey rakh dey agar-che sab mulkon waley un par chadh dauden (to unhen halak nahin kar saken gey). albatta ye aapas main eik doosrey ko halak karengey aur eik doosrey ko qaid karengey.'' (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya) ''mujhey apni ummat par gumrah imaamon ka khauf hai. aur jab un main eik baar talwaar pad gaee to qiyamat tak uthai nahin jaeygi. aur us waqt tak qiyamat nahin aaeygi jab tak ke meri ummat ke kuchh qabaayel mushrikon ke sath na mil jaeyn aur kuchh qabiley buton ki ibadat na kerney lagen. aur an-qareeb meri ummat mein kazaab aur jhootey log zahir hongey, unki tadaad tees hogi, un mein se her eik ka dawa hoga ke wo Nabi hai. halanke main khaatim-un-nabiyeen hun, merey baad koi Nabi nahin. aur meri ummat ka eik giroh hamesha haq par rahega . . . ibne Esa ne kaha . . . haq par ghalib rahega . unka koi mukhalif unka kuchh nahin bigaad sakega yahan tak ke Allah ka faisla aa jaeyga.''"
4253,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne tumhen teen baaton se amaan di hai : tumhara Nabi tum par badduaa nahin kerega ke tum sab halak ho jao aur ye ke ehale-batil ehale-haq par ghalib nahin aa sakengey (yani kulli aur majmui taur par) aur ye ke tum log gumrahi par jama nahin hogey.''"
4254,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam ki chakki paintees, chhattis ya saintees tak chaley gi. phir agar halak huey to halaak honey walon ki yehi raah hogi aur agar unka deen qaaim raha to sattar saal tak qaaim rahega. ''Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, maine arz kiya : kya ye sattar saal mazeed hongey ya sabiqa muddat bhi us mein shamil hai? aapney farmaya : ''guzishta muddat ke sath. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain (Rabae bin Harash '' حا '' baghair nuqtey ke hai) jisney kharraash '' خا '' nuqtey ke sath kaha usney ghalati ki hai."
4255,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''waqt qarib aa jaeyga (ya sikud jaeyga) ilm kam ho jaey, fitney uth khadey hongey, bakheeli dal di jaeygi aur ''burj'' badh jaeyga.'' puchha gaya aey Allah ke Rasool ! ''burj'' kya hoga? aapney farmaya : ''qatl hi qatl.''"
4256,"Janab Muslim bin Abu-Bakra apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb fitna hoga us mein letaa hua aadmi baithney waley se behtar hoga , aur baitha hua khadey huey ki nisbat behtar hoga , aur khada honey wala chalney waley se behtar hoga , aur chalney wala daudhney waley se behtar hoga. kehtey hain ke maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? aapney farmaya : '' jiskey paas oont hon wo apney oonton mein chala jaey. aur jiski bakriyan hon wo apni bakriyon mein chala jaey. aur jiski kheti ho wo apni zameen mein chala jaey.'' kaha ke jiskey paas un mein se kuchh na ho? aapney farmaya : ''wo apni talwaar ley aur uski dhaar ko pathar par maarey (usey kund kar dey) aur phir jahan tak ho sakey (fitney mein shareek honey se) bachney ki koshish karey.''"
4257,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees mein bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha, maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! farmaiye ke agar koi fitna parwar merey ghar mein dakhil ho jaey aur mujhey qatl kerney ke liye apna haath badhaey? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hazrat Adam (Alahissalaam) ke (us) bete ki manind ho jana . . . Yazid bin Khalid ne ye aayat padhi. . ۔ (لئن بسطت إلي يدك - - - - ) ''agar to ne merey qatl ke liye haath badhaya to main tujhey qatl kerney ke liye apna haath teri taraf nahin badhaun ga , beshak main Allah Rabbul-A'alameen se darta hun.''"
4258,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna . . . to Abu-Bakra wali hadees ka kuchh hissey bayan kiya. farmaya : ''iskey maqtooleen sabhi aag mein jaeyngey . . . '' is riwayat mein hai, Wabeesa ne puchha : aey ibne-Masood ! ye Kab hoga? unhoney farmaya : ''ye haraj (qatl aur fitnon) ke din hongey, jab koi aadmi apney sath baithney waley se bhi aman mein na hoga.'' maine kaha : aap mujhey kya hukm detey hain agar meri zindagi mein ye din aagaey to? unhoney kaha : apni zaban band aur apney haath ko rokey rakhna aur apney ghar ki koi chatai bin jana . phir jab Saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) qatl huey to merey dil mein achcha khayal aaya (ke kahin ye wohi fitna na ho) to main Sawwar hua yahan tak ke dimashq pahuncha aur Janab khuraim bin Faatik (Raziallahu anhu) se mila . maine unko sab bataya , to unhoney Allah ki qasam khai jiskey siwa koi mabud nahin ke usney bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi suna hai jaisey ke mujhey Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya tha."
4259,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beshak qiyamat se pehley fitney hongey itney siyah kaley jaisey andheri raat (yani haq aur batil gadmad ho jaeyga) aadmi subah ko momin hoga aur shaam ko kafir. shaam ko momin hoga aur subah ko kafir . us mein baitha hua khadey honey waley ki nisbat behtar hoga aur chalney wala daudhney waley se behtar hoga. so apni kamanon ko taud dena aur taanton ko kaat phenkna aur apni talwaaron ko patharon par maarna (aur kund kar lena) agar koi tum par chadh aaye to Hazrat Adam Alehissalam ke behtar bete ki manind ho jana.''
4260,"Abdur-Rehman bin Sumra kehtey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka haath pakdey Madiney ke eik raastey par chal raha tha ke achcha eik sar dekha jo kisi cheez par latkaayaa gaya tha. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehney lagey : uska qatil bada bad-bakht hai. jab aagey badh gaey to boley . . . mera khayal hai ke ye bada bad-bakht hai. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai, farmatey they : ''jo aadmi meri ummat ke kisi aadmi ko qatl kerney ke liye chaley to usey usi tarah karna chahiye yani apni gardan badha dey. qatil dozakh mein hai aur maqtool jannat mein. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain is riwayat ko Sauri ne b-waaste Aun , Abdur-Rehman bin Sameer ya Sameera se riwayat kiya hai aur Lais bin Abi Sulaim ne ba-waaste  Aun , Abdur-Rehman bin Sameera se. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain mujhey Hasan bin Ali ne bayan kiya ke Abu-Waleed ne ye hadees Abu-Awaana se riwayat ki aur kaha ke meri kitab mein (raawi ka naam) ibne Sabra darj hai jabkey doosrey raawi Samura aur kaee Sameera kehtey hain aur ye kalam Abu-Waleed ka hai."
4261,"Saiyedna Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Abu-Zar !'' maine jawab mein kaha : main hazir hun aey Allah ke Rasool ! hazir hun. aur hadees bayan ki . is mein hai : ''tera kya haal hoga jab log maren-gey aur ghar eik ghulam ki qeemat mein milega?'' murad hai qabr. maine arz kiya : Allah aur uska Rasool behtar jantey hain. ya kaha : jo Allah aur uska Rasool merey liye pasand farmaeyn. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sabr karna.'' phir mujh se farmaya : ''aey abu-Zar !'' maine kaha : main hazir hun. aapney farmaya : ''tera kya haal hoga jab ye maqam ''ehjarizzait'' khoon mein doob jaeyga?'' maine kaha : jo Allah aur uska Rasulullah merey liye pasand farmaeyn. aapney farmaya : ''wahin chaley jana jahan ke tum ho.'' maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main apni talwaar lekar apney kandhey par na rakh lun? aapney farmaya : ''tab to to unhi logon mein shareek ho jaeyga.'' maine arz kiya : aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? farmaya : ''apney ghar mein padey rehna.'' maine kaha : agar koi merey ghar mein ghus aaye to? aapney farmaya : ''agar tujhey andesha ho ke talwaar ki chamak se tum saham jao-gey to apney chehrey par kapda dal lena , wo tumharey aur apney gunah samet lega. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat mein Hammad bin Zaid ke alawa aur kisi ne Mish'as bin Tareef ka zikr nahin kiya."
4262,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey aagey ghata top andheri raat ki manind fitney hain. aadmi un mein subah ko momin , shaam ko kafir aur shaam ko momin aur subah ko kafir hoga , baitha hua un mein khadey honey waley ki nisbat behtar hoga aur khada hua chalney waley se behtar hoga aur chalney wala daudhney waley se behtar hoga.'' Sahaba ne kaha : to aap hamen kya farmatey hain? aapney farmaya : ''tum apney gharon ke taat bin jana.'' (yani un mein kisi tarah se koi hissey na lena.)"
4263,"Hazrat Miqdad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''bila-shuba intehai khush bakht hai wo insan jo fitnon se bacha raha. bada khush bakht hai wo insan jo fitnon se bacha raha , bada khush bakht hai wo insan jo fitnon se bacha raha . aur jo un mein mubtala kiya gaya phir usney sabr kiya, to uska kya kehna.''"
4264,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb fitna hoga behra , gunga aur andha . jisney us mein jhaankaa , fitna uski taraf maael hoga. aur us mein zaban chalaanaa aisey hoga jaisey ke talwaar chalaanaa.''"
4265,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb fitna barpa hoga jo sab arbon ko halak kar daley ga, uskey maqtool jahannam mein jaeyngey. us mein zaban se bolnaa talwaar chalaney se bhi sakht hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is riwayat ko Sauri ne ba-waaste Lais , Taaus se aur usney A'ajam se riwayat kiya."
4266,Muhammad bin Esa bin Tabaa'a ne bayan kiya ke Abdullah bin Abdul-Quddoos ne Ziyad ke ta'aruf mein usey ''Ziyad Simen Kosh'' kaha : yani chaandi ke kanon wala . (kanon ki safedi ki wajeh se ye naam rakha.)
4267,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb aisey hoga ke musalman ka behtareen maal uski bakriyan hongi jin ka peechha kartey huey wo pahadon ki chotiyon aur barish ki jagahon mein phirta rahega, apney deen ki hifazat mein fitnon se bhagna chahta hoga.''"
4268,"Ahnaf bin Qais kehtey hain : main nikalna chahta tha ke (ladaai jamal mein) qitaal mein hissey lun ke mujhey Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) mil gaey, to unhoney kaha : wapis lot jao maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farma rahey they : ''jab do musalman talwaarein lekar eik doosrey ke aamney samney hotey hain to qatil aur maqtool (dono) jahannami bin jatey hain.'' kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye to qatil hua magar maqtool ka kya qusur hua? aapney farmaya : ''usney bhi apney sathi ko qatl kerney ka irada kar rakha tha.''"
4269,"Ayub ne Hasan se apni sanad se mukhtisaar taur par mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Muhammad bin Mutawakkil ka eik aur bhai tha Husain, lekin wo zaeef hai."
4270,"Khalid bin Dahqaan ne bayan kiya ke ham log ghazwae-qustuntuniya mein zulqiya maqam par they ke ehale Palestine ka eik bada raees aaya jisey wo log pehchantey they aur uska naam Haani bin Kulsoom bin Shareek kinaani tha. usney Abdullah bin Ubai Zakariya ko salam kaha aur wo unka maqam aur martaba pehchanta tha. Khalid ne bayan kiya : phir hamen Abdullah bin Abu-Zakariya ne hadees bayan ki, kaha : maine Umme-Dardaa se suna wo kehti thin ke maine Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''har gunah umeed hai ke Allah usey maaf farma dega , magar wo jo shirk ki haalat mein mar gaya ya jisney jaan bojh-kar kisi momin ko qatl kiya ho.'' to Haani bin Kulsoom ne kaha : maine Mehmood bin Rabeea se suna, wo Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey they ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna, aapney farmaya : '' jisney kisi momin ko qatl kiya aur bilaa wajah zulm se qatl kiya tu Allah uska koi amal qubul nahin kerega nafl na farz.'' Khalid ne hamein kaha : phir ibne Abu-Zakariya ne mujhey ba-waaste Umme-Dardaa . . . Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin hamesha bada halka-fulka aur achhey aamaal ki taufeeq mein rehta hai jab tak ke kisi haram khoon ka murtakib (mujrim) na ho, jab wo uska murtakib ho jata hai to us taufeeq se mehroom ho jata hai.'' aur Haani bin Kulsoom ne ba-waaste Mehmood bin Rabeea, Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bilkul usi ke misl (jaisi) riwayat ki."
4271,Khalid bin Dahqaan ne kaha : maine Yahya bin Yahya Ghassaani se (اعتبط بقتله) ka mafhoom puchha to unhoney kaha ke jo log fitney mein qitaal kartey hain aur eik un mein se kisi ko qatl kar deta hai aur phir samajhta hai ke wo haq aur hidayat par tha aur us amal par Allah se istighfar nahin karta hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain. . . aur mazeed kaha ke (فاعتبط) ka mafhoom hai ke khoon bahaataa hai khoob bahana.
4272,"Khaarija bin Zaid kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se is jagah suna tha, wo kehtey they ke Sura Nisaa ki ye aayat kareema (ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاؤه جهنم خالدا فيها) Sura Furqaan ki aayat (والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر ولا يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق) se chhe maah baad nazil hui hai."
4273,"Saeed bin Jubair kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se sawal kiya to unhoney kaha : jab Sura Furqaan ki aayat : (والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر ولا يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق) nazil hui to Makka ke mushrekin ne kaha : (ab hamarey emaan laney ka kya fayda) ham ne nahaq jaanen qatl ki hain, Allah ke sath doosrey maboodon ko pukara hai aur badkaariyon ka irtikab bhi kiya hai. . tab Allah ne ye irshad nazil kiya : (إلا من تاب وآمن وعمل عملا صالحا فأولئك يبدل الله سيئاتهم حسنات) ye aayaten inhi mushrekin ke haq mein hain. (Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne) kaha : lekin Sura Nisaa ki aayat : (ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاؤه جهنم . . ۔) ''aisey (musalman) shakhs ke liye hai jo Islaami ehkam janta hai phir kisi momin ko jaan bojh kar qatl karta hai to uski saza jahannam hai aur uski tauba bhi qubul nahin. . ۔''  Saeed ne kaha ke maine (Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki) is baat ka Mujahid se zikr kiya to unhoney kaha : magar jo shakhs naadim ho jaey. (to uski tauba qubul hogi. In-Sha-Allah )"
4274,"Saeed bin Jubair ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se Sura Furqaan ki aayat : (والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر . ۔ ۔) ki tafseer mein bayan kiya ke ye mushrekin ke baarey mein hai, isike sath ye bhi nazil hua : (يا عبادي الذين أسرفوا على أنفسهم لا تقنطوا من رحمة الله) ''aey merey bando ! jinhon ne apni jaanon par ziyadti ki hai tum Allah ki rehmat se na-umeed na ho jao.''"
4275,"Saeed bin Jubair , Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke Sura Nisaa ki aayat : (ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا) (النساء : 93) ''aur jo koi kisi momin ko jaan bojh kar qatl karey.'' ko kisi aayat ne mansookh nahin kiya hai."
4276,Janab Abu-Mujliz se marwi (bayan) hai ke (ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاؤه جهنم) (النساء : 93) ''jaan-boojh kar qatl karne wale qatil ki saza yehi hai ke hamesha jahannam mein rahey.'' aur agar Allah usey maaf karna chahey to kar sakta hai.
4277,Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke aapney fitney ke honey ka zikr farmaya aur uski heybat-naaki bayan ki. ham ne arz kiya ya logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar ye hamen pahunch gaya to halak kar daleyga. aapney farmaya : ''hergiz nahin. us main tumhen qatl ho jana hi kafi hoga.''  Saeed kehtey hain : phir maine apney bhaiyon ko dekha ke qatl ho gaey.
4278,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri is ummat par Allah ki rehmat hai, aakhirat mein is par azab nahin, iska azab duniya mein fitnon, zalzalon aur qatl ki soorat mein hai.''"
